Main features
 - multi-profile â€“ user can set up 3 different server profiles to connect to
 - control MPD server (play,stop,pause,prev,next,repeat,random,consume)
 - view,navigate queue
 - clear queue
 - create/edit/save/load playlists
 - browse music by files and add to current queue
 - browse music by aritsts and albums and add/replace current queue
 - can auto play associated stream via XBMC when MPD server is currently playing/streaming
